    <item>
      <title>日本对日元的不温不火警告在国际货币基金组织之前再次助长日元疲软</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/japan-s-finance-minister-warns-on-yen-ahead-of-imf-g7-meetings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本财务大臣警告称，如有需要，他已准备好在外汇市场采取行动，但并未兑现最大威胁，这一言论在日元隔夜跌至 34 年来的新低后，加剧了日元再度疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/japan-s-finance-minister-warns-on-yen-ahead-of-imf-g7-meetings</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 00:33:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Codelco寻求合作以帮助提高陷入困境的铜产量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/codelco-eyes-partnerships-to-help-boost-ailing-copper-production</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着智利国有铜业巨头希望从产量下滑和债务激增中恢复过来，Codelco 正在探索与私营部门建立更多合作伙伴关系。]]></description>
